[SPEAKER_02] Dobro pobijeduje zlo.

583
01:06:14,639 --> 01:06:15,519
[SPEAKER_02] To je uvijek ovoga.

584
01:06:15,920 --> 01:06:17,920
[SPEAKER_02] Nit vodilja i to doista je tako.

585
01:06:18,320 --> 01:06:18,960
